{"tid":1971432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗公園男子被8人圍毆　惡漢持刀恐嚇再自稱黑幫逃逸","createTime":"2020-04-14T01:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T02:01:35.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f05c05e4a10667ddfb02de7f37dddc463c43d26","tid":1971432,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xxko1Aw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxko1Aw.jpg&h=d3ba02a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日(14日)凌晨1時許，姓郭(30歲)男子在深水埗荔枝角道733號深水埗公園內，與一名惡漢因肢體碰撞問題爭執，期間被對方7男1女圍毆；另一名惡漢自稱為黑幫成員，並亮出生果刀指嚇後逃去。郭面部及腳部被毆傷，報案求助，救護員將他送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方將案件列「自稱三合會成員」、「藏有攻擊性武器」及「普通襲擊」，深水埗警區刑事調查隊正追緝該7男1女，他們案發時皆穿黑色衫褲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200414/mobile/bkn-20200414040945847-0414_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200414%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200414040945847-0414_00822_001.html&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=121c0156\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200414/mobile/bkn-20200414040945847-0414_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ea79d31a9d887224e44e73789334e18f16aadbeb","tid":1971432,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T01:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6531595918d68abd6cc07babfe6cac546f0c7e6c","tid":1971432,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"走住黎屌<br />\n冇撚用"},{"pid":"e790346ada061d18462973c04753497a82d46a37","tid":1971432,"uid":194281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"黑衣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc6763211d5cb6ad215e2553b722c02eaf9b70a","tid":1971432,"uid":286232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T02:01:35.000Z"